    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. The chassis is well-sorted, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already addressed. Power is transferred via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M-differential lock. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing inspection to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. Currently riding on a refreshed suspension with poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in response and reduced lateral deflection. A driver-focused example that balances mechanical purity with daily usability.",
      "price": 32500.0,
