    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and small surface scratches consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows only light bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat. All electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule\u2014full service records are available for your review. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. This is a turn-key car that has been genuinely cared for, offering a premium, reliable driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
