      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, reliable, and ready for many more adventures with a new owner. It runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway! If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been treated with care, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
