      "description": "Available is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a mid-engine masterpiece powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six engine. This unit features VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis retains its signature poise with a well-sorted MacPherson strut suspension and hydraulic power steering providing exceptional feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes a new water pump and drive belt. While the exterior shows minor road-rash typical of a driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are robust, with the four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors offering firm pedal feel. A mechanically honest example for the purist seeking telepathic handling.",
